         <meta.section type="apiInfo"/>
      </appinfo>
      <documentation>
         Extensions must implement &lt;code&gt;org2.eclipse.php.ui.preferences.IPHPPreferencePageBlock&lt;/code&gt;. Abstract class 
&lt;code&gt;AbstractPHPPreferencePageBlock&lt;/code&gt; can be used for convenience.
